Cross-Engine Dependencies
SIG integrates with but does not own:
MUX — external data access
PIE — insight synthesis
DAT — execution signals
SIM — scenario analysis
GGP — audit and governance

Completion Criteria
SIG documentation is complete when:
NS-SIG-000 → NS-SIG-014 exist
Signal trust and provenance are explicit
Noise and poisoning are detectable
Downstream engines can reason about signal quality

